Class UserCred

java.lang.Object
  com.seatunity.model.UserCred

public class UserCred
extends java.lang.Object

Model-class to hold the user-credential values. The server response correxponding this class is: <br> {<br> "success": "true", <br> "token": "gobbledygook", <br> "language": "en", <br> "firstname": "Jane", <br> "lastname": "Shepherd", <br> "gender": "unspecified", <br> "live_in": "Normandy", <br> "age": "122", <br> "profession": "Citadel Council Spectre", <br> "status": "my status", <br> "seating_pref": "small_talk", <br> "image_url": "path/to/profile_pic.jpg" <br> } <br>
